## Active thread: Phase 1 — activation + top-up funnel (highest-ROI)

Phase 0 done (2026-04-24 evening). Next: build the funnel the unit economics
actually depend on.

**Phase 1 scope**:
1. `/activate?iccid=...` landing page. Reads ICCID (from Amazon box QR code),
   looks up the bundled plan, prompts account creation + auto-renew opt-in.
2. `/top-up?iccid=...` — top-up by ICCID, login required only at checkout.
3. In-app `/app/my-sims` — prominent auto-renew toggle + accurate usage bar.
4. Transactional emails (Resend via Netlify function): 80% used, plan ending
   in 3 days, auto-renew success/failure.
5. Auto-renew disclosure copy (ROSCA + CA SB-313 compliant). Draft into
   `docs/AUTO_RENEW_DISCLOSURE.md`.

Do not touch home page, country pages, or device pages yet — that's Phase 2/3.

